author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Fenerbahce signs advertising agreement with Yandex
text:
Aug 18 Fenerbahce Futbol AS :
* Signs advertising agreement with Yandex
* According to the agreement revenue will be gained by number of searches performed on www.fbyandex.com.tr
* The maximum duration of the contract is 3 years and will be revised based on performance
